><link href="vladimirvoevodsky.xml" type="local" vladimirvoevodsky="addr">Vladimir Voevodsky</link></author> </authors> <title>IAS Special Year on Univalent Foundations</title>  <meta name="venue">Institute for Advanced Study</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>A Special Year on Univalent Foundations of Mathematics was held in 2012-13 at the Institute for Advanced Study, School of Mathematics, organized by <link href="steveawodey.xml" type="local" addr="steveawodey" title="Steve Awodey">Steve Awodey</link>, <link href="thierrycoquand.xml" type="local" addr="thierrycoquand" title="Thierry Coquand">Thierry Coquand</link>, and <link href="vladimirvoevodsky.xml" type="local" addr="vladimirvoevodsky" title="Vladimir Voevodsky">Vladimir Voevodsky</link>. The following people were the official participants:</p><ul><li>Peter Aczel</li>
